2026 Regular Session
SENATE CONCURRENT RESOLUTION NO. 71
BY SENATOR SEABAUGH
COMMENDATIONS. Commends and congratulates Kathy Holloway upon receiving the
2026 Dave Dixon Louisiana Sports Leadership Award and on being inducted into the 2026
class of the Louisiana Sports Hall of Fame.
1 A CONCURRENT RESOLUTION
2 To commend and congratulate Kathy Holloway upon receiving the 2026 Dave Dixon
3 Louisiana Sports Leadership Award and on being inducted into the 2026 class of the
4 Louisiana Sports Hall of Fame.
5 WHEREAS, the Louisiana Sports Hall of Fame in Natchitoches, Louisiana, each year
6 collaborates with the Louisiana Sports Writers Association in selecting a limited number of
7 sports figures who embody the character, skill, and talent worthy of being named to the
8 Louisiana Sports Hall of Fame; and
9 WHEREAS, the Dave Dixon Louisiana Sports Leadership Award is a prestigious
10 honor presented annually by the Louisiana Sports Hall of Fame to an individual who has
11 played a decisive role as a sports leader or administrator benefitting Louisiana and has
12 brought credit to Louisiana on the national and international stage; and
13 WHEREAS, Kathy Holloway has been selected for the 2026 Dave Dixon Louisiana
14 Sports Leadership Award from the Louisiana Sports Hall of Fame and inducted into the 2026
15 Louisiana Sports Hall of Fame Induction Class; and
16 WHEREAS, Kathy Holloway is the fourth woman recipient of the Dave Dixon
17 Louisiana Sports Leadership Award; and
18 WHEREAS, Kathy Stewart Holloway, a native of Alexandria, Louisiana, has
